snippet.title: Amber Heard Reacts To Johnny Depp Winning In Court...
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Reacts To Johnny Depp Winning In Court...
They say that how you go and respond to a situation shows your character. Especially when it's a situation that you personally have no control over...and it doesn't go your way. And when it comes to the court case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, though they are trying hard to prove their sides of the issue, how things are ruled is based upon a judge (currently) and so who knows how it's all going to play out. But recently, Johnny Depp has been getting some key victories in court, and Amber has responded...by drinking a lot. We'll break it down for you, be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation with Johnny Depp and Amber Heard and how it's all starting to go to Heard's head...and her liver. Are you surprised that she decided to go this particular path after Johnny started getting victories and praise? Do you think this will just go and get her wanting to win even more than before? What will she do now once the court case starts? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
